<br>
Ok....<br>
<br>
YOU LIVE IN THE FUCKING DESERT!!!  It's the desert!!  You know why you are starving?  You live on sand.  There is no good vegetation growing in the sand.  You know why there's no animals there to eat?  THEY LEFT BECAUSE IT&quot;S THE FUCKING DESERT.  Why don't you get a clue from the zebras and get the hell out of the desert?<br>
<br>
What is the desert?  SAND.  What was the desert 1000 years ago?  SAND.  What will the desert be in 1000 years from now?  SAND.<br>
<br>
Get the hell out.  You've had plenty of time already.  Oh yea, and quit fucking if your kids are starving.  I think there's a good few American families that would benefit from that advice as well.<br>
<br>
Maybe I'm wrong.<br>
